## Comprehensive Agent Protocol (AUTO-TRIGGER)

> **MANDATORY**: Apply at the start of every Cursor session on any medinovai repo.
> Full protocol: `memory/context/agent-protocol.md`

### Session Startup
- **First session** (no `progress.md`): Create `init.sh` + `progress.md` + `features.json` (all `"passes": false`) + initial commit. STOP.
- **Subsequent sessions**: Run `pwd` → read git log + `progress.md` → run `init.sh` + tests → pick ONE feature where `"passes": false`.

### Non-Negotiable Rules
1. EXACTLY ONE feature per session — never one-shot a full app
2. NEVER delete or modify existing tests
3. "Done" = Playwright/browser end-to-end visual verification passed
4. Feature branches only — never commit to `main`
5. After feature: `features.json` (passes: true) + `progress.md` update + git commit + STOP

### Healthcare Compliance Gate
Every clinical feature requires before `"passes": true`:
- [ ] HIPAA/GDPR data handling verified
- [ ] Audit trail complete and tested
- [ ] Fail-safe default on all error paths
- [ ] FDA 21 CFR Part 11 / ISO 13485 / IEC 62304 gates passed
